SECOND REGULAR SESSION
HOUSE COMMITTEE SUBSTITUTE FOR
SENATE BILL NO. 1019
103RD GENERAL ASSEMBLY
4774H.04C JOSEPH ENGLER, Chief Clerk
AN ACT
To repeal sections 96.192, 96.196, 191.1146, 206.110, 324.009, 334.108, 345.050, 376.1000,
376.1012, 376.1017, 632.305, 632.489, 632.492, 632.495, 632.504, and 632.520,
RSMo, and to enact in lieu thereof thirty-one new sections relating to health care, with
penalty provisions.
Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the state of Missouri, as follows:
Section A. Sections 96.192, 96.196, 191.1146, 206.110, 324.009, 334.108, 345.050,
2 376.1000, 376.1012, 376.1017, 632.305, 632.489, 632.492, 632.495, 632.504, and 632.520,
3 RSMo, are repealed and thirty-one new sections enacted in lieu thereof, to be known as
4 sections 96.192, 96.196, 191.1146, 192.021, 197.708, 206.110, 206.158, 208.149, 324.009,
5 334.108, 345.050, 376.417, 376.1000, 376.1012, 376.1017, 376.1280, 407.3007, 632.305,
6 632.489, 632.492, 632.495, 632.504, 632.520, 632.580, 632.585, 632.590, 632.593, 632.595,
7 632.600, 632.605, and 632.610, to read as follows:
96.192. 1. The board of trustees of any hospital authorized under subsection 2 of this
